{"tid":1166480,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日地震 手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子終於來了（心心眼emoji）","createTime":"2019-05-22T12:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T13:16:16.000Z","uid":134997,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c97f50f8e46dd9dac9c88b770147cac00f0820f7","tid":1166480,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924276.jpg&h=0447ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924275.jpg&h=8ac8e8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924274.jpg&h=4662e826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4c0a90090cb3208f49f6f11c31c6e457913602","tid":1166480,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"巴打住幾多樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ca29bc65e78c6e22756115d176101cf2cfb0a3","tid":1166480,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4c0a90090cb3208f49f6f11c31c6e457913602","tid":1166480,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"巴打住幾多樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"咁多樓，九龍新界無得避。。。"},{"pid":"b7325805ab647612f931d45a841625627e844480","tid":1166480,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"放到過期。唔取捨得丟，食到肚痛。"}]}